{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Adventure across the lush Hawaiian island of Maikai and lead a team of chefs through the challenges of running a pop-up restaurant. Build new relationships and rediscover the bonds that make a kitchen feel like home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333930/extras/KSA_Gameplay.gif?t=1736901998\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333930/extras/KSA_Header_1.png?t=1736901998\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Befriend and recruit a cast of colorful chefs, each with their unique specialties. As you guide them through tropical cooking venues, you\u2019ll uncover their personal stories and witness the bonds that form within this close-knit community. As the chefs collaborate and support one another, their bonds deepen and friendships grow\u2026some may even find unexpected romance.      </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333930/extras/KSA_Drew_Hina.gif?t=1736901998\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333930/extras/KSA_Header_2.png?t=1736901998\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whip up some mouthwatering Hawaiian dishes as you explore Maikai's various venues and overcome challenges! Serve Spam Musubi, Mac Salad, Loco Moco, and more. Craft your menu and customize your recipes by adding your own Twists. Optimize your kitchen layout, upgrade your appliances, and level up your chefs' abilities to fully master every kitchen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333930/extras/Kitchens.gif?t=1736901998\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333930/extras/KSA_Header_3.png?t=1736901998\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Need a break from the kitchen? Strengthen your bond with your team and enjoy what the island has to offer. Go on a fishing trip or a nature hike. Each mini-game lets you grow your relationship with the chefs you befriend on your journey.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333930/extras/KSA_Kai_Kala.gif?t=1736901998\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333930/extras/KSA_Header_4.png?t=1736901998\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as either Kai or Kala, two siblings on their quest to bring their family\u2019s restaurant back to life. Along the way, you\u2019ll complete meaningful side quests, experiment with recipes, and craft dishes as unforgettable as the people you\u2019ll meet. Start as the new eatery on the island and grow your restaurant into a local gem.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">On Maikai, cooking is more than just preparing meals. It\u2019s about growing relationships and embracing the spirit of community.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333930/extras/KSA_Header_5.png?t=1736901998\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cozy Cooking RPG</strong> - The narrative focus of visual novel meets strategic kitchen management. Level up characters, customize kitchen layouts, and build relationships to uncover stories.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Over 30 Different Kitchens</strong> - Cook at beaches, restaurants, malls, food trucks, resorts, and more, all set against the beauty of a lush Hawaiian island.\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Wholesome and Heartwarming Story</strong> - A journey of food, family, and discovering joy in the connections that bring people together.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>No Stress Kitchen Management</strong> - Play at your own pace with a timer that pauses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Grow Relationships</strong> - Build stronger bonds between party members or find love with different romantic endings!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Mini-games</strong> - Participate in island activities like fishing and hiking with fellow chefs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>3 Different Difficulty Settings</strong> - Turn off all timers and relax with Cozy mode or test your skills with Hard Boiled mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333930/extras/KSA_Header_6.png?t=1736901998\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Follow along on our development journey, give feedback, or help playtest on Discord!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333930/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736901998","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333930/page.bg.jpg?t=1736901998","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333930/0ac8f4b46985c2cd6d2e561d5dc4acff4089bf5b/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736901998","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2333930/0ac8f4b46985c2cd6d2e561d5dc4acff4089bf5b/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736901998","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"F